summary: A tower that is worth fighting for
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ffe599][size=4][b][size=6][color=#f1c232]Another Fabulous & Unnecessary mod by fredlaus:[/color] [color=#cc0000]#2[/color][/size][/b]
[color=#ffd966][size=4]Why unnecessary mods?
Because they make your game beautiful.
You get more place to live, stack your stuff and house your followers
- and increase your self-esteem dramatically.[size=4] He, he.[/size][/size][/color]
---------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#b6b6b6]Mistwatch Twin Tower is a new place for the player to stack stuff and house followers.
This one you'll have to fight for.
There are 3 floors.
The 2 lower floors are inhabited by Mistwatch bandits.
They are involved in producing weapon and armory instead of kidnapping rich young, imperial girls.
In my game they are my friends.
The Top Floor, however, you have no other choice than to fight your way through a large Thalmore group, some with very strong powers in magic or weaponry.
The way you choose to enter the Top Floor is crucial for your survival and success.
The Top Floor is really a top floor and something worth fighting for.
My other Unnecessary mods:[/color][/size][/color][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75776/]
[/url][color=#ffe599][size=4][color=#b6b6b6][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75769/]Tropical Docks of Solitude
[/url][color=#ffe599][size=4][color=#b6b6b6][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75778/]Mistwatch Supply Ship
[/url][color=#ffe599][size=4][color=#b6b6b6][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75797/]TS The MIne
[/url][color=#ffe599][size=4][color=#b6b6b6][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75815/]TS Free Mine Village[/url][/color][/size][/color][/color][/size][/color][/color][/size][/color][/color][/size][/color][/size][color=#ffe599][size=4][color=#b6b6b6]
This mod is not dependent on Tropical Skyrim. [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33017/?]I am though.[/url][/color][/size]
I guess you will see some of [u]Tamira's[/u] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22018]New Plants[/url] as well.
